metadata.name: Frozen Whispers
metadata.description:
Falling snowflakes paint a dreamy air,
Anticipation lingers, an enchanting affair.
Her eyes, a portrait of longing so deep,
A smile of yearning, a secret to keep.
Through the flurry, a figure draws near,
A man with an umbrella, erasing her fear.
In this wintry scene, their paths collide,
A tableau suspended, emotions tied.
